  tags:["dubai photography spots","best photo spots dubai","instagram spots dubai 2026","dubai golden hour photography","dubai night photography","burj khalifa photo spot","dubai photography guide","best time photograph dubai","dubai sunrise photography","dubai drone photography"],
  title:"Dubai Photography Guide — 20 Best Spots & Exact Timings",
  metaTitle:"Dubai Photography Guide 2026 | 20 Best Spots & When to Shoot",
